author: Holly Ellyatt
title: Coronavirus 'likely' to have come from animals — not a lab, WHO says
description: Evidence suggests the coronavirus originated in bats in China in late 2019 and it was not manipulated or constructed in a laboratory, the World Health Organization said Tuesday.
content:
Evidence suggests the coronavirus originated in bats in China in late 2019 and was not manipulated or made in a laboratory, the World Health Organization (WHO) said Tuesday.
